{"type":"message","id":"184e31ac","parentId":"36e6018b","timestamp":"2026-04-20T09:13:31.674Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_93f259be86ab4137b021be8b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"do_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/qqbot/\" \"qqbot/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw-weixin/\" \"openclaw-weixin/\"\n\n# Commit and push\ncd \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\nif [ -n \"$(git status --porcelain)\" ]; then\n  git config user.email \"backup@openclaw\"\n  git config user.name \"OpenClaw Backup\"\n  git add -A\n  git commit -m \"Full backup $DATE_DIR $(date '+%H:%M')\"\n  git push origin \"$GIT_REF\"\n  echo \"[$(date)] Backup pushed to GitHub\"\nelse\n  echo \"[$(date)] No changes, skipping commit\"\nfi"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":23,"aggregated":"do_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/qqbot/\" \"qqbot/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw-weixin/\" \"openclaw-weixin/\"\n\n# Commit and push\ncd \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\nif [ -n \"$(git status --porcelain)\" ]; then\n  git config user.email \"backup@openclaw\"\n  git config user.name \"OpenClaw Backup\"\n  git add -A\n  git commit -m \"Full backup $DATE_DIR $(date '+%H:%M')\"\n  git push origin \"$GIT_REF\"\n  echo \"[$(date)] Backup pushed to GitHub\"\nelse\n  echo \"[$(date)] No changes, skipping commit\"\nfi","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776676411661}}
{"type":"message","id":"63501608","parentId":"184e31ac","timestamp":"2026-04-20T09:13:48.399Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to add a step to send a Feishu message after the backup. I'll use the Feishu API with the bot's access token to send a message to the user's OpenID.\n\nLet me first get an access token for the Feishu bot, then send a message. The approach:\n1. Get tenant access token using appId + appSecret\n2. Send message to user's open_id\n\nThe user's OpenID is: ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\n\nLet me figure out the exact API call needed. The appId is `cli_a93650c6fc785bce` and appSecret is `I6PGaAjXEqMW81COlOcRzc7zpdd2qqOV`.\n\n\nNow I'm constructing the curl commands to authenticate and send the message. I'll get the access token first, then use it to post a text message to the user with a summary of what was backed up.\n\nBut I should verify the API endpoint format for Feishu's send message v1 API, since the correct host should be `open.feishu.cn` rather than a generic API endpoint. The curl request would need to include the access token as a bearer credential, the recipient's open_id, message type specification, and the actual text content in the request body."},{"type":"text","text":"我来在脚本末尾加一段发送飞书通知的逻辑：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3d3a95cc5435432ea1cbc773","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"# Commit and push\ncd \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\nif [ -n \"$(git status --porcelain)\" ]; then\n  git config user.email \"backup@openclaw\"\n  git config user.name \"OpenClaw Backup\"\n  git add -A\n  git commit -m \"Full backup $DATE_DIR $(date '+%H:%M')\"\n  git push origin \"$GIT_REF\"\n  echo \"[$(date)] Backup pushed to GitHub\"\n\n  # ── Send Feishu notification ──────────────────────────────────────\n  APP_ID=\"cli_a93650c6fc785bce\"\n  APP_SECRET=\"I6PGaAjXEqMW81COlOcRzc7zpdd2qqOV\"\n  USER_OPEN_ID=\"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n\n  # Get tenant access token\n  TOKEN_RESP=$(curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"app_id\\\":\\\"$APP_ID\\\",\\\"app_secret\\\":\\\"$APP_SECRET\\\"}\")\n  ACCESS_TOKEN=$(echo $TOKEN_RESP | python3 -c \"import json,sys; print(json.load(sys.stdin).get('tenant_access_token',''))\")\n\n  if [ -n \"$ACCESS_TOKEN\" ]; then\n    BACKUP_TIME=$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n    curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=open_id\" \\\n      -H \"Authorization: Bearer $ACCESS_TOKEN\" \\\n      -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n      -d \"{\n        \\\"receive_id\\\":\\\"$USER_OPEN_ID\\\",\n        \\\"msg_type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\n        \\\"content\\\":\\\"{\\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"✅ OpenClaw 备份已完成\\\\n📅 时间：$BACKUP_TIME\\\\n📁 仓库：openclaw-backup\\\\\\\"}\\\"\n      }\" > /dev/null 2>&1\n    echo \"[$(date)] Feishu notification sent\"\n  else\n    echo \"[$(date)] Failed to get access token, skipping Feishu notification\"\n  fi\n  # ── End Feishu notification ────────────────────────────────────────\nelse\n  echo \"[$(date)] No changes, skipping commit\"\nfi","oldText":"# Commit and push\ncd \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\nif [ -n \"$(git status --porcelain)\" ]; then\n  git config user.email \"backup@openclaw\"\n  git config user.name \"OpenClaw Backup\"\n  git add -A\n  git commit -m \"Full backup $DATE_DIR $(date '+%H:%M')\"\n  git push origin \"$GIT_REF\"\n  echo \"[$(date)] Backup pushed to GitHub\"\nelse\n  echo \"[$(date)] No changes, skipping commit\"\nfi"}],"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-backup/backup.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776676411675,"responseId":"0635213bc5d0b760138d6e627517f011"}}
