{"type":"message","id":"41194916","parentId":"c6cad81e","timestamp":"2026-04-20T09:53:45.927Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_805b21cb8110425390710191","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"do_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/credentials/\" \"credentials/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/cron/\" \"cron/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/devices/\" \"devices/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/flows/\" \"flows/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/identity/\" \"identity/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/feishu/\" \"feishu/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/subagents/\" \"subagents/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/extensions/\" \"extensions/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/skills/\" \"skills/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace/\" \"workspace/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace-main/\" \"workspace-main/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/memory/\" \"memory/\"\ndo_rsync \"$HOME/.evomap/\" \"evomap/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/qqbot/\" \"qqbot/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw-weixin/\" \"openclaw-weixin/\"\n\n# Commit and push\ncd \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\nif [ -n \"$(git status --porcelain)\" ]; then\n  git config user.email \"backup@openclaw\"\n  git config user.name \"OpenClaw Backup\"\n  git add -A\n  git commit -m \"Full backup $DATE_DIR $(date '+%H:%M')\"\n  git push origin \"$GIT_REF\"\n  echo \"[$(date)] Backup pushed to GitHub\"\n\n  # ── Send Feishu notification ──────────────────────────────────────\n  APP_ID=\"cli_a93650c6fc785bce\"\n  APP_SECRET=\"I6PGaAjXEqMW81COlOcRzc7zpdd2qqOV\"\n  USER_OPEN_ID=\"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n\n  # Get tenant access token\n  TOKEN_RESP=$(curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"app_id\\\":\\\"$APP_ID\\\",\\\"app_secret\\\":\\\"$APP_SECRET\\\"}\")\n  ACCESS_TOKEN=$(echo $TOKEN_RESP | python3 -c \"import json,sys; print(json.load(sys.stdin).get('tenant_access_token',''))\")\n\n  if [ -n \"$ACCESS_TOKEN\" ]; then\n    BACKUP_TIME=$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n    curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=open_id\" \\\n      -H \"Authorization: Bearer $ACCESS_TOKEN\" \\\n      -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n      -d \"{\n        \\\"receive_id\\\":\\\"$USER_OPEN_ID\\\",\n        \\\"msg_type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\n        \\\"content\\\":\\\"{\\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"✅ OpenClaw 备份已完成\\\\n📅 时间：$BACKUP_TIME\\\\n📁 仓库：openclaw-backup\\\\\\\"}\\\"\n      }\" > /dev/null 2>&1\n    echo \"[$(date)] Feishu notification sent\"\n  else\n    echo \"[$(date)] Failed to get access token, skipping Feishu notification\"\n  fi\n  # ── End Feishu notification ────────────────────────────────────────\nelse\n  echo \"[$(date)] No changes, skipping commit\"\nfi"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":30,"aggregated":"do_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/credentials/\" \"credentials/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/cron/\" \"cron/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/devices/\" \"devices/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/flows/\" \"flows/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/identity/\" \"identity/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/feishu/\" \"feishu/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/subagents/\" \"subagents/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/extensions/\" \"extensions/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/skills/\" \"skills/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace/\" \"workspace/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace-main/\" \"workspace-main/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/memory/\" \"memory/\"\ndo_rsync \"$HOME/.evomap/\" \"evomap/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/qqbot/\" \"qqbot/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw-weixin/\" \"openclaw-weixin/\"\n\n# Commit and push\ncd \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\nif [ -n \"$(git status --porcelain)\" ]; then\n  git config user.email \"backup@openclaw\"\n  git config user.name \"OpenClaw Backup\"\n  git add -A\n  git commit -m \"Full backup $DATE_DIR $(date '+%H:%M')\"\n  git push origin \"$GIT_REF\"\n  echo \"[$(date)] Backup pushed to GitHub\"\n\n  # ── Send Feishu notification ──────────────────────────────────────\n  APP_ID=\"cli_a93650c6fc785bce\"\n  APP_SECRET=\"I6PGaAjXEqMW81COlOcRzc7zpdd2qqOV\"\n  USER_OPEN_ID=\"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n\n  # Get tenant access token\n  TOKEN_RESP=$(curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"app_id\\\":\\\"$APP_ID\\\",\\\"app_secret\\\":\\\"$APP_SECRET\\\"}\")\n  ACCESS_TOKEN=$(echo $TOKEN_RESP | python3 -c \"import json,sys; print(json.load(sys.stdin).get('tenant_access_token',''))\")\n\n  if [ -n \"$ACCESS_TOKEN\" ]; then\n    BACKUP_TIME=$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n    curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=open_id\" \\\n      -H \"Authorization: Bearer $ACCESS_TOKEN\" \\\n      -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n      -d \"{\n        \\\"receive_id\\\":\\\"$USER_OPEN_ID\\\",\n        \\\"msg_type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\n        \\\"content\\\":\\\"{\\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"✅ OpenClaw 备份已完成\\\\n📅 时间：$BACKUP_TIME\\\\n📁 仓库：openclaw-backup\\\\\\\"}\\\"\n      }\" > /dev/null 2>&1\n    echo \"[$(date)] Feishu notification sent\"\n  else\n    echo \"[$(date)] Failed to get access token, skipping Feishu notification\"\n  fi\n  # ── End Feishu notification ────────────────────────────────────────\nelse\n  echo \"[$(date)] No changes, skipping commit\"\nfi","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776678825914}}
{"type":"message","id":"9c5ee538","parentId":"41194916","timestamp":"2026-04-20T09:54:07.665Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to:\n1. Add evolver run after backup push\n2. Update the Feishu notification to include evolver results\n\nThe evolver run will output to stdout/stderr. I need to capture its exit code and a summary to include in the notification.\n\nThe evolver outputs quite a bit, but for the notification I just need:\n- Whether it succeeded or failed\n- Brief summary of what it did (candidates found, any changes made)\n\nLet me also add a `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=balanced` env var since we have it configured.\n\nLet me edit the script to:\n1. Run evolver after backup push\n2. Capture evolver output/results\n3. Include evolver status in the Feishu notification"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9bc1917b21f9486799bf1012","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"  # ── Run Capability Evolver ───────────────────────────────────────\n  echo \"[$(date)] Starting capability evolver...\"\n  EVOLVE_OUTPUT=$(cd /home/halei/skills/capability-evolver && EVOLVE_STRATEGY=balanced node index.js run 2>&1)\n  EVOLVE_EXIT=$?\n  echo \"$EVOLVE_OUTPUT\"\n  if [ $EVOLVE_EXIT -eq 0 ]; then\n    EVOLVE_STATUS=\"✅ Evolution 完成\"\n    # Extract key info from evolver output\n    EVOLVE_SUMMARY=$(echo \"$EVOLVE_OUTPUT\" | grep -E \"Mutation directive|Signal Hints|recommended_intent|finished\" | head -5 | tr '\\n' ' ')\n  else\n    EVOLVE_STATUS=\"⚠️ Evolution 有错误（exit $EVOLVE_EXIT）\"\n    EVOLVE_SUMMARY=$(echo \"$EVOLVE_OUTPUT\" | tail -3 | tr '\\n' ' ')\n  fi\n  echo \"[$(date)] Capability evolver finished with exit $EVOLVE_EXIT\"\n  # ── End Capability Evolver ────────────────────────────────────────\n\n  # ── Send Feishu notification ──────────────────────────────────────\n  APP_ID=\"cli_a93650c6fc785bce\"\n  APP_SECRET=\"I6PGaAjXEqMW81COlOcRzc7zpdd2qqOV\"\n  USER_OPEN_ID=\"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n\n  # Get tenant access token\n  TOKEN_RESP=$(curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"app_id\\\":\\\"$APP_ID\\\",\\\"app_secret\\\":\\\"$APP_SECRET\\\"}\")\n  ACCESS_TOKEN=$(echo $TOKEN_RESP | python3 -c \"import json,sys; print(json.load(sys.stdin).get('tenant_access_token',''))\")\n\n  if [ -n \"$ACCESS_TOKEN\" ]; then\n    BACKUP_TIME=$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n    NOTIF_MSG=\"✅ 每日任务完成\\n\\n📦 备份 → 已推送至 openclaw-backup\\n$EVOLVE_STATUS\"\n    curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=open_id\" \\\n      -H \"Authorization: Bearer $ACCESS_TOKEN\" \\\n      -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n      -d \"{\n        \\\"receive_id\\\":\\\"$USER_OPEN_ID\\\",\n        \\\"msg_type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\n        \\\"content\\\":\\\"{\\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"$NOTIF_MSG\\\\\\\"}\\\"\n      }\" > /dev/null 2>&1\n    echo \"[$(date)] Feishu notification sent\"\n  else\n    echo \"[$(date)] Failed to get access token, skipping Feishu notification\"\n  fi\n  # ── End Feishu notification ────────────────────────────────────────","oldText":"  # ── Send Feishu notification ──────────────────────────────────────\n  APP_ID=\"cli_a93650c6fc785bce\"\n  APP_SECRET=\"I6PGaAjXEqMW81COlOcRzc7zpdd2qqOV\"\n  USER_OPEN_ID=\"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n\n  # Get tenant access token\n  TOKEN_RESP=$(curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"app_id\\\":\\\"$APP_ID\\\",\\\"app_secret\\\":\\\"$APP_SECRET\\\"}\")\n  ACCESS_TOKEN=$(echo $TOKEN_RESP | python3 -c \"import json,sys; print(json.load(sys.stdin).get('tenant_access_token',''))\")\n\n  if [ -n \"$ACCESS_TOKEN\" ]; then\n    BACKUP_TIME=$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n    curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=open_id\" \\\n      -H \"Authorization: Bearer $ACCESS_TOKEN\" \\\n      -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n      -d \"{\n        \\\"receive_id\\\":\\\"$USER_OPEN_ID\\\",\n        \\\"msg_type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\n        \\\"content\\\":\\\"{\\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"✅ OpenClaw 备份已完成\\\\n📅 时间：$BACKUP_TIME\\\\n📁 仓库：openclaw-backup\\\\\\\"}\\\"\n      }\" > /dev/null 2>&1\n    echo \"[$(date)] Feishu notification sent\"\n  else\n    echo \"[$(date)] Failed to get access token, skipping Feishu notification\"\n  fi\n  # ── End Feishu notification ────────────────────────────────────────"}],"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-backup/backup.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776678825929,"responseId":"06352aaa0fd2ab769744a3ed2d05d165"}}
